HitTitle: Improve/extend description of auction item(s) on pictures
Answer 1: This beautiful watch manufactured by Puma has very many different features on it.  Apart from it's sleek black band, the face of this watch is interchangeable, matching your team or country you want to represent. Not only does this watch serve as a stopwatch, it also lights up which is perfect for using at night.  This watch is made with stainless steel.  The watch is also water resistant. Model number Pu910751011.
